            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "聯合航空警告油價上漲將對航空業造成壓力",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/FSohemaPO_oD8FNraAnbyA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/indicatornews_6_M_1440048362.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com – <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-yga='{\"yLinkElement\":\"context_link\",\"yModuleName\":\"content-canvas\",\"yLinkText\":\"聯合航空\",\"ySubModuleName\":\"anchor_text\",\"yHasCommerce\":false}' data-ylk=\"slk:聯合航空;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/聯合航空\">聯合航空</a>控股公司(NASDAQ:UAL)警告稱,與伊朗衝突相關的燃料成本上升正開始對航空業造成壓力,儘管旅遊需求依然強勁。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">聯合航空執行長Scott Kirby在給員工的訊息中表示,該航空公司正在為油價長期處於高位的時期做準備,這可能推高營運成本,並迫使公司調整運力和定價策略。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Kirby表示,聯合航空正在為油價可能升至每桶175美元並在2027年之前維持高位的情境做規劃,不過他補充說情況可能不會那麼嚴重。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-26497c0f-13fe-3ea4-b688-22434d92758a-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他表示,該航空公司將在短期內削減約5%的計劃運力,包括減少離峰時段航班和暫停部分國際航線,以應對更高的燃料成本。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">他補充說,聯合航空將繼續進行長期投資,包括飛機交付和基礎設施擴建,若油價持續處於高位,這將使該航空公司獲得競爭優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這一警告發布之際,全球石油市場因中東緊張局勢升級而持續波動。分析師表示,航空公司的短期前景將取決於供應中斷持續多久,以及原油價格是否能夠穩定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8A%E6%BC%B2%E5%B0%87%E5%B0%8D%E8%88%AA%E7%A9%BA%E6%A5%AD%E9%80%A0%E6%88%90%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-144207601.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-21 23:36:28",
